    <h1>Chapter 8: Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)</h1>

    <!-- REVIEW: This chapter includes comparative/best-practice defaults (e.g., token ranges and “often outperforms”). Validate with citations or label as heuristic if needed; do not adjust values without sources. -->

